{"type":"message","id":"66d9e152","parentId":"60e77e1a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:50:17.413Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a0349dcc01b545b0bdd5075c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Session: 2026-03-09 06:57:45 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main-stock:feishu:stock:direct:ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\n- **Session ID**: 42baac45-91f5-467f-9698-f9efff898e51\n- **Source**: feishu\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d2da719118b2dcd02535f460e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d2da719118b2dcd02535f460e]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: tushare-data技能如何使用\nassistant: **📊 tushare-data 技能使用说明**\n\n**1. 前提条件：**\n- 需要先注册 tushare.pro 账号并获取 token\n- Token 配置在环境变量 `TUSHARE_TOKEN` 中\n\n**2. 使用步骤：**\n\n```bash\n# 第一步：注册获取 token\n访问 https://tushare.pro/register 注册账号\n\n# 第二步：设置 token\nexport TUSHARE_TOKEN=你的_token_值\n\n# 第三步：在代码中使用\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\n\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 查询股票数据示例\ndf = pro.daily(ts_code='601857.SH', start_date='20260301', end_date='20260309')\n```\n\n**3. 可用功能：**\n- ✅ 日 K 线行情（历史 + 实时）\n- ✅ 分钟线数据（1/5/15/30/60min）\n- ✅ 基本面财务数据\n- ✅ 资金流向\n- ✅ 龙虎榜、涨停板\n- ✅ 宏观数据（GDP、CPI、利率等）\n\n**4. 当前状态：**\n我的环境还没有配置 tushare token，如需使用需要先设置环境变量。\n\n需要我帮您记录这个需求，后续配置 token 后再使用？\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d2d986ac80b3fd98d2cc8b844\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:32 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d2d986ac80b3fd98d2cc8b844]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: 环境已经配置了 tushare token\nassistant: 老板，tushare-data 技能已可用！\n\n📊 **中国石油 (601857.SH) 最新行情**\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 收盘价 | **12.30 元** |\n| 涨跌额 | -0.39 元 |\n| 涨跌幅 | **-3.07%** |\n| 开盘价 | 12.38 元 |\n| 最高价 | 12.65 元 |\n| 最低价 | 12.07 元 |\n| 成交量 | 510.39 万手 |\n| 成交额 | 6,266.54 万元 |\n\n**数据来源**：tushare.pro（沪深交易所官方数据）\n\n---\n\n**💡 tushare 还能查询：**\n- ✅ 任意股票历史/实时 K 线\n- ✅ 所有自选股批量行情\n- ✅ 资金流向、龙虎榜\n- ✅ 财务指标、基本面数据\n\n需要帮您查看其他股票或进行对比分析吗？\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d2d2d9b080b3c9efaddd80d66\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d2d2d9b080b3c9efaddd80d66]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: 查看我的股票\nassistant: 老板，您的**自选股今日行情**：\n\n📊 **A 股部分 (2026-03-09)**\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 收盘价 | 涨跌额 | 涨跌幅 | 成交量 (万手) |\n|------|------|--------|--------|--------|--------------|\n| 601857 | 中国石油 | **12.30** | -0.39 | **-3.07%** ⬇️ | 510.39 |\n| 601808 | 中海油服 | **18.74** | -1.06 | **-5.35%** ⬇️ | 71.11 |\n| 600256 | 广汇能源 | **6.80** | +0.04 | **+0.59%** ⬆️ | 436.13 |\n| 600583 | 海油工程 | **7.55** | -0.15 | -1.95% ⬇️ | 171.38 |\n| 000852 | 石化机械 | **8.70** | -0.38 | -4.18% ⬇️ | 56.93 |\n| 600547 | 山东黄金 | **46.02** | -0.83 | -1.77% ⬇️ | 44.72 |\n| 601069 | 西部黄金 | **37.01** | -0.20 | -0.54% ⬇️ | 23.64 |\n| 600988 | 赤峰黄金 | **39.94** | -0.40 | -0.99% ⬇️ | 48.65 |\n| 000975 | 银泰黄金 | **30.49** | -0.50 | -1.61% ⬇️ | 35.54 |\n| 002716 | 金贵银业 | **14.87** | +0.07 | **+0.47%** ⬆️ | 161.73 |\n| 601899 | 紫金矿业 | **37.10** | -0.57 | -1.51% ⬇️ | 253.95 |\n\n**今日表现**：\n- 🟢 上涨：广汇能源、金贵银业\n- 🔴 下跌：其余 9 只股票（普遍回调）\n- 📉 跌幅最大：中海油服 (-5.35%)\n\n**数据来源**：tushare.pro\n\n需要我帮您分析某只股票的详细走势吗？\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d2ea4e98b0b3717f6186ec4ca\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:35 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d2ea4e98b0b3717f6186ec4ca]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: 实时行情\nassistant: 📊 **tushare-pro 说明**\n\ntushare 提供的是**收盘后的历史数据**（T+1），非盘中实时行情。\n\n您刚才看到的行情数据：\n- ✅ **真实可靠** - 来自沪深交易所官方\n- ⏰ **更新时间** - 每日 17:00 后更新当日收盘数据\n- 📈 **最新日期**：2026-03-09（交易日结束后）\n\n---\n\n**💻 如需盘中实时行情**，请通过以下方式：\n\n| 方式 | 链接 |\n|------|------|\n| **东方财富网** | https://quote.eastmoney.com/sz601857.html |\n| **同花顺** | https://www.10jqka.com.cn/stock/601857.html |\n| **券商交易软件** | 您的开户券商 APP/PC 端 |\n\n**⚡ tushare 优势**：\n- 批量查询所有自选股\n- 历史 K 线数据\n- 财务指标分析\n- 资金流向统计\n\n需要我帮您用 tushare 做哪些分析？\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d2e03e9d10b4b7b782564ea28\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d2e03e9d10b4b7b782564ea28]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=315 参考这个，看下如何获取实时数据\nassistant: 📊 **tushare 实时行情接口说明**\n\n根据官方文档，tushare 提供 **实时日线行情 (rt_k)** 接口：\n\n---\n\n**✅ 如何获取实时数据：**\n\n```python\nimport tushare as ts\nimport os\n\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 方式 1: 查询单个股票实时行情\ndf = pro.rt_k(ts_code='601857.SH')\nprint(df)\n\n# 方式 2: 批量查询（支持通配符）\ndf = pro.rt_k(ts_code='3*.SZ,6*.SH,0*.SZ,9*.BJ')\n\n# 返回字段包括：\n# - close: 最新价\n# - open/high/low/pre_close: 开盘/最高/最低/昨收\n# - vol/amount: 成交量/成交额\n# - bid_price1/ask_price1: 买卖盘口\n# - trade_time: 交易时间\n```\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 注意事项：**\n- 该接口需要**单独申请权限**（积分要求）\n- 非交易时段可能不返回数据\n- 需要在交易日 9:30-15:00 之间调用\n\n---\n\n让我帮您测试一下这个接口能否使用：\n\n\nassistant: 🎉 **成功获取实时行情！**\n\n📊 **中国石油 (601857.SH) - 实时行情**\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 🕐 **最新价** | **12.94 元** ⬆️ (+0.64) |\n| 📈 **涨跌幅** | **+5.20%** 🔴 |\n| 🔼 今开 | 13.48 元 |\n| 🔺 最高 | 13.48 元 |\n| 🔻 最低 | 12.91 元 |\n| ⚖️ 昨收 | 12.30 元 |\n| 📊 成交量 | 76,242.18 万手 |\n| 💵 成交额 | 1,005,277.69 万元 |\n\n---\n\n✅ **rt_k 接口已成功调用**\n- 数据来源：**tushare.pro 实时日线接口**\n- 更新时间：盘中实时更新\n- 权限状态：已开通\n\n需要我帮您批量查询其他自选股的实时行情吗？\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d2fc470488b3fd3829bd694c3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:39 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d2fc470488b3fd3829bd694c3]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: 查看我的股票\nassistant: ⚠️ **rt_k 实时接口有调用限制**\n\ntushare pro 的实时日线接口 (**rt_k**) 权限：**每分钟最多 1 次访问**\n\n这意味着：\n- ❌ 无法批量查询多只股票\n- ✅ 可以逐个查询（需要等 1 分钟冷却）\n\n---\n\n**💡 建议方案：**\n\n1. **使用 tushare 日 K 线 (daily)** - 收盘数据，无限次查询\n   ```python\n   pro.daily(ts_code='601857.SH', start_date='20260306')\n   ```\n\n2. **直接访问财经网站** - 盘中实时行情\n   - 东方财富：https://quote.eastmoney.com/sz601857.html\n   - 同花顺：https://www.10jqka.com.cn/stock/601857.html\n\n3. **分批查询** - 每次间隔 1 分钟以上\n\n---\n\n您想：\n- 🔹 用 daily 接口查看最新收盘数据？\n- 🔹 逐个手动查询某几只股票的实时行情？\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d2800e44c4b4aa07e7fcd8bce\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 14:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d2800e44c4b4aa07e7fcd8bce]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: 实时行情\nassistant: ⚠️ **实时行情接口调用次数已达上限**\n\ntushare rt_k 实时日线接口的权限限制：\n- **中国石油 (601857)**: 每小时最多 1 次 ✅ 刚才查过\n- **其他股票**: 每分钟最多 1 次 ❌ 已达上限\n\n---\n\n**📊 今日最新收盘数据**（可用 daily 接口）:\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 收盘价 | 涨跌幅 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|\n| 601857 | 中国石油 | 12.30 | -3.07% |\n| 601808 | 中海油服 | 18.74 | -5.35% |\n| 600256 | 广汇能源 | 6.80 | +0.59% |\n| 600583 | 海油工程 | 7.55 | -1.95% |\n| 000852 | 石化机械 | 8.70 | -4.18% |\n| 600547 | 山东黄金 | 46.02 | -1.77% |\n| 601069 | 西部黄金 | 37.01 | -0.54% |\n| 600988 | 赤峰黄金 | 39.94 | -0.99% |\n| 000975 | 银泰黄金 | 30.49 | -1.61% |\n| 002716 | 金贵银业 | 14.87 | +0.47% |\n| 601899 | 紫金矿业 | 37.10 | -1.51% |\n\n**数据来源**：tushare.pro (daily 日 K 线)\n\n---\n\n💡 **如需盘中实时行情**，建议通过：\n- 东方财富网查看您的自选股列表\n- 券商交易软件的实时看板\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773107417412}}
{"type":"message","id":"db6e0193","parentId":"66d9e152","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:50:17.416Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1f3c1c83417645df924f2a80","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n获取自选股实时行情数据\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport time\n\n# Tushare Token\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = \"68442b378fd881f50cc6ae402e7277b6f46061bcc7b1df17b4ca6318\"\nWATCHLIST_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt\")\nOUTPUT_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\")\n\ndef get_tushare_data(code):\n    \"\"\"通过 Tushare rt_k 接口获取实时行情\"\"\"\n    try:\n        import tushare as ts\n        \n        ts.set_token(TUSHARE_TOKEN)\n        pro = ts.pro_api()\n        \n        # 标准化代码格式\n        ts_code = code\n        if code.endswith('.SH') or code.endswith('.SZ') or code.endswith('.HK') or code.endswith('.US'):\n            pass\n        elif code.startswith('6') or code.startswith('0'):\n            ts_code = f\"{code}.SH\" if code.startswith('6') else f\"{code}.SZ\"\n        elif code.endswith('.HK'):\n            ts_code = code\n        else:\n            ts_code = f\"{code}.US\" if code.isupper() else f\"{code}.SH\"\n        \n        # 尝试 rt_k 实时接口\n        try:\n            df = pro.rt_k(ts_code=ts_code)\n            if not df.empty:\n                row = df.iloc[0]\n                return {\n                    'code': code.split('.')[0] if '.' in code else code,\n                    'name': row.get('name', code),\n                    'price': float(row.get('close', 0)),\n                    'pct_chg': float(row.get('pct_chg', 0)),\n                    'price_change': float(row.get('close', 0)) - float(row.get('pre_close', 0)),\n                    'vol': float(row.get('vol', 0)),\n                    'amount': float(row.get('amount', 0)),\n                    'trade_time': row.get('trade_time', datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'))\n                }\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"rt_k 失败 {ts_code}: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        \n        # 回退到 daily 接口\n        trade_date = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n        df = pro.daily(ts_code=ts_code, trade_date=trade_date)\n        if not df.empty:\n            row = df.iloc[0]\n            return {\n                'code': code.split('.')[0] if '.' in code else code,\n                'name': row.get('name', code),\n                'price': float(row.get('close', 0)),\n                'pct_chg': float(row.get('pct_chg', 0)),\n                'price_change': float(row.get('close', 0)) - float(row.get('pre_close', 0)),\n                'vol': float(row.get('vol', 0)),\n                'amount': float(row.get('amount', 0)),\n                'trade_time': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n            }\n        \n        return None\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Tushare 错误 {code}: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        return None\n\ndef load_watchlist():\n    \"\"\"加载自选股列表\"\"\"\n    stocks = []\n    if os.path.exists(WATCHLIST_FILE):\n        with open(WATCHLIST_FILE, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            for line in f:\n                line = line.strip()\n                if line and '|' in line:\n                    parts = line.split('|')\n                    stocks.append({'code': parts[0], 'name': parts[1] if len(parts) > 1 else parts[0]})\n    return stocks\n\ndef main():\n    print(f\"📊 开始获取实时行情 - {datetime.now()}\")\n    \n    # 清空输出文件\n    with open(OUTPUT_FILE, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        pass\n    \n    stocks = load_watchlist()\n    results = []\n    \n    for i, stock in enumerate(stocks):\n        code = stock['code']\n        name = stock['name']\n        \n        print(f\"[{i+1}/{len(stocks)}] 获取 {code} {name}...\", end=\" \")\n        \n        data = get_tushare_data(code)\n        \n        if data:\n            results.append(data)\n            change_symbol = \"🔴\" if data['pct_chg'] >= 0 else \"🟢\"\n            print(f\"✅ ¥{data['price']:.2f} ({data['pct_chg']:+.2f}%) {change_symbol}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"❌ 失败\")\n        \n        # 控制请求频率 (rt_k 限制每分钟 1 次)\n        if i < len(stocks) - 1:\n            time.sleep(1.5)\n    \n    # 写入结果\n    with open(OUTPUT_FILE, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(\"代码 | 名称 | 现价 | 涨跌幅 | 成交量 | 成交额 | 时间\\n\")\n        for r in results:\n            vol_str = f\"{r['vol']/10000:.2f}万\" if r['vol'] > 10000 else f\"{r['vol']:.2f}\"\n            amount_str = f\"{r['amount']/100000000:.1f}亿\" if r['amount'] > 100000000 else f\"{r['amount']/10000:.1f}万\"\n            f.write(f\"{r['code']}|{r['name']}|{r['price']:.2f}|{r['pct_chg']:+.2f}%|{vol_str}|{amount_str}|{r['trade_time']}\\n\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n✅ 完成！共获取 {len(results)} 只股票数据\")\n    print(f\"📁 保存至：{OUTPUT_FILE}\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773107417415}}
{"type":"message","id":"c33764a3","parentId":"db6e0193","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:50:21.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the setup. Let me check what day it is and whether the market is open. Today is Tuesday, March 10th, 2026, 9:50 AM (Asia/Shanghai). This is during market hours (9:30-15:00 for A-shares).\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Check if today is a trading day (not weekend/holiday)\n2. Clear the realtime-data.txt file\n3. Fetch real-time data using the existing script or tushare\n4. Filter based on alert rules\n5. Send alerts via feishu if any stocks meet the criteria\n\nLet me first check if there's a script to determine if today is a trading day, and then execute the data fetch. I'll also look at the filter-and-alert.py script to see if I can reuse it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9b75c756408943408a914a4d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/filter-and-alert.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8bad594d98e34364a8f86e6d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/fetch-realtime-daily.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773107417416}}
{"type":"message","id":"fecdd405","parentId":"c33764a3","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:50:21.419Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9b75c756408943408a914a4d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n过滤预警数据并发送飞书通知\n\"\"\"\n\nimport subprocess\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nINPUT_FILE = \"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\"\nOUTPUT_FILE = \"/home/openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-data.txt\"\n\n# Alert rules\nALERT_DROP_THRESHOLD = -3.0  # Generic: drop > 3%\nALERT_RISE_THRESHOLD = 5.0   # Generic: rise > 5%\n\n# Special rules for 中国石油 (601857)\nSPECIAL_STOCK_RULES = {\n    '601857': {\n        'name': '中国石油',\n        'rise_threshold': 2.0,   # Rise > 2% triggers\n        'drop_threshold': -1.0   # Drop > 1% triggers\n    }\n}\n\ndef parse_stock_data(line):\n    \"\"\"解析股票数据行\"\"\"\n    parts = line.strip().split('|')\n    if len(parts) >= 5:\n        return {\n            'code': parts[0],\n            'name': parts[1],\n            'price': parts[2],\n            'change_pct': float(parts[3].replace('%', '').replace('+', '')),\n            'price_change': parts[4],\n            'time': parts[5] if len(parts) > 5 else ''\n        }\n    return None\n\ndef check_alert_rules(stock_data):\n    \"\"\"检查是否触发预警规则\"\"\"\n    code = stock_data['code']\n    change = stock_data['change_pct']\n    \n    # Check special rules first\n    if code in SPECIAL_STOCK_RULES:\n        rule = SPECIAL_STOCK_RULES[code]\n        if change > rule['rise_threshold'] or change < rule['drop_threshold']:\n            return True\n        return False\n    \n    # Check generic rules\n    if change > ALERT_RISE_THRESHOLD or change < ALERT_DROP_THRESHOLD:\n        return True\n    \n    return False\n\ndef main():\n    print(f\"🔍 开始过滤预警数据 - {datetime.now()}\")\n    \n    # Read data\n    with open(INPUT_FILE, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        lines = f.readlines()\n    \n    if len(lines) <= 1:\n        print(\"⚠️  数据文件为空或格式错误\")\n        return\n    \n    # Skip header line\n    header = lines[0].strip()\n    data_lines = lines[1:]\n    \n    alert_results = []\n    \n    for line in data_lines:\n        if not line.strip():\n            continue\n        \n        stock = parse_stock_data(line)\n        if stock:\n            if check_alert_rules(stock):\n                alert_results.append(stock)\n                print(f\"⚠️  {stock['code']} {stock['name']}: {stock['price']} ({stock['change_pct']:+.2f}%) - 触发预警!\")\n    \n    # Sort by change percentage (descending)\n    alert_results.sort(key=lambda x: x['change_pct'], reverse=True)\n    \n    print(f\"\\n{'='*60}\")\n    print(f\"✅ 过滤完成！触发预警：{len(alert_results)} 只\")\n    \n    if alert_results:\n        # Write alert data\n        with open(OUTPUT_FILE, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            f.write(header + \"\\n\")\n            for r in alert_results:\n                f.write(f\"{r['code']}|{r['name']}|{r['price']}|{r['change_pct']:+.2f}%|{r['price_change']}|{r['time']}\\n\")\n        \n        print(f\"📁 预警数据保存至：{OUTPUT_FILE}\")\n        \n        # Build Feishu message\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        message_lines = [\n            \"⚠️ 股价预警通知\",\n            f\"时间：{timestamp}\",\n            \"\",\n            \"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间 |\",\n            \"|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\"\n        ]\n        \n        for r in alert_results:\n            time_str = r['time'].split(' ')[1][:5] if r['time'] else timestamp.split(' ')[1][:5]\n            message_lines.append(f\"| {r['code']} | {r['name']} | {r['price']} | {r['change_pct']:+.2f}% | {r['price_change']} | {time_str} |\")\n        \n        message_lines.extend([\n            \"\",\n            \"⚙️ 预警规则\",\n            \"• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\",\n            \"• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\",\n            \"• 中国石油：涨幅>2% 或 跌幅>1% → 触发\"\n        ])\n        \n        message = \"\\n\".join(message_lines)\n        \n        print(f\"\\n📤 准备发送飞书预警通知...\")\n        print(f\"接收用户：ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\")\n        \n        # Send via Feishu using openclaw CLI\n        cmd = ['openclaw', 'message', 'send', '--channel', 'feishu', '--account', 'stock', \n               '--message', message, '--target', 'ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5']\n        \n        try:\n            result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=30)\n            if result.returncode == 0:\n                print(f\"✅ 飞书通知发送成功!\")\n            else:\n                print(f\"❌ 发送失败：{result.stderr}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"❌ 发送异常：{e}\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 无触发预警的股票，无需发送通知\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773107421418}}
{"type":"message","id":"d108eb04","parentId":"fecdd405","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:50:21.422Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8bad594d98e34364a8f86e6d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n获取自选股实时行情数据 (使用 Tushare daily 接口)\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nimport time\n\n# Tushare Token\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN', 'd5dffac476638f230dbe209bef04cd97b100c2dd3ddd10ddf85bc33d')\nWATCHLIST_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt\")\nOUTPUT_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\")\n\ndef get_tushare_daily(code):\n    \"\"\"通过 Tushare daily 接口获取最新行情\"\"\"\n    try:\n        import tushare as ts\n        \n        ts.set_token(TUSHARE_TOKEN)\n        pro = ts.pro_api()\n        \n        # 标准化代码格式\n        ts_code = code\n        if code.endswith('.SH') or code.endswith('.SZ') or code.endswith('.HK') or code.endswith('.US'):\n            pass\n        elif code.startswith('6') or code.startswith('9'):\n            ts_code = f\"{code}.SH\"\n        elif code.startswith('0') or code.startswith('3'):\n            ts_code = f\"{code}.SZ\"\n        elif code.startswith('68'):\n            ts_code = f\"{code}.SH\"  # STAR market\n        elif '.HK' in code.upper():\n            ts_code = code.replace('.HK', '.HK').upper() if not code.endswith('.HK') else code\n        elif code.isupper() and len(code) <= 5:\n            ts_code = f\"{code}.US\"\n        else:\n            ts_code = f\"{code}.SH\"\n        \n        # 获取今天和昨天的数据\n        today = datetime.now()\n        for days_back in range(5):  # 最多回溯 5 天\n            trade_date = (today - timedelta(days=days_back)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\n            \n            try:\n                df = pro.daily(ts_code=ts_code, trade_date=trade_date)\n                if not df.empty:\n                    row = df.iloc[0]\n                    close = float(row.get('close', 0))\n                    pre_close = float(row.get('pre_close', 0))\n                    pct_chg = float(row.get('pct_chg', 0))\n                    \n                    if close > 0:\n                        price_change = close - pre_close\n                        return {\n                            'code': code.split('.')[0] if '.' in code else code,\n                            'name': row.get('name', code),\n                            'price': close,\n                            'pct_chg': pct_chg,\n                            'price_change': price_change,\n                            'vol': float(row.get('vol', 0)),\n                            'amount': float(row.get('amount', 0)),\n                            'trade_time': trade_date\n                        }\n            except Exception as e:\n                continue\n        \n        return None\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Tushare 错误 {code}: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        return None\n\ndef load_watchlist():\n    \"\"\"加载自选股列表\"\"\"\n    stocks = []\n    if os.path.exists(WATCHLIST_FILE):\n        with open(WATCHLIST_FILE, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            for line in f:\n                line = line.strip()\n                if line and '|' in line:\n                    parts = line.split('|')\n                    stocks.append({'code': parts[0], 'name': parts[1] if len(parts) > 1 else parts[0]})\n    return stocks\n\ndef main():\n    print(f\"📊 开始获取实时行情 - {datetime.now()}\")\n    \n    stocks = load_watchlist()\n    results = []\n    \n    for i, stock in enumerate(stocks):\n        code = stock['code']\n        name = stock['name']\n        \n        print(f\"[{i+1}/{len(stocks)}] 获取 {code} {name}...\", end=\" \")\n        \n        data = get_tushare_daily(code)\n        \n        if data:\n            results.append(data)\n            change_symbol = \"🔴\" if data['pct_chg'] >= 0 else \"🟢\"\n            print(f\"✅ ¥{data['price']:.2f} ({data['pct_chg']:+.2f}%) {change_symbol}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"❌ 失败\")\n        \n        # 控制请求频率\n        if i < len(stocks) - 1:\n            time.sleep(0.5)\n    \n    # 写入结果 (使用 watchlist 中的名称)\n    timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n    stock_names = {s['code']: s['name'] for s in stocks}\n    with open(OUTPUT_FILE, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(\"代码 | 名称 | 现价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间\\n\")\n        for r in results:\n            price_str = f\"¥{r['price']:.2f}\"\n            change_str = f\"{r['pct_chg']:+.2f}%\"\n            change_amt = f\"¥{r['price_change']:.2f}\"\n            name = stock_names.get(r['code'], r['name'])\n            f.write(f\"{r['code']}|{name}|{price_str}|{change_str}|{change_amt}|{timestamp}\\n\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n✅ 完成！共获取 {len(results)} 只股票数据\")\n    print(f\"📁 保存至：{OUTPUT_FILE}\")\n    \n    return results\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773107421420}}
{"type":"message","id":"1572775a","parentId":"d108eb04","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:50:25.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I have a clear understanding of the workflow. Let me now:\n\n1. First check if today is a trading day (Tuesday, March 10th, 2026 - should be a trading day)\n2. Clear the realtime-data.txt file\n3. Run the fetch script to get real-time data\n4. Run the filter script to check alert rules\n5. Send notifications if needed\n\nLet me check if there's a trading day checker and then execute the workflow. First, let me check if the market is open today.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_995e04fa8c584984ad904792","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = 'd5dffac476638f230dbe209bef04cd97b100c2dd3ddd10ddf85bc33d'\nts.set_token(TUSHARE_TOKEN)\npro = ts.pro_api()\n\n# Check trading calendar for today\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\ndf = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=today, end_date=today, is_open='1')\nif not df.empty:\n    print('MARKET_OPEN')\nelse:\n    print('MARKET_CLOSED')\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773107421422}}
